{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015dvUwsCAhSpnuHCtJBBfes","type":"tool_result","content":"<persisted-output>\nOutput too large (50.8KB). Full output saved to: C:\\Users\\rjega\\.claude\\projects\\C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis\\9ed88350-d5e8-4179-8856-45e53162fa46\\tool-results\\toolu_015dvUwsCAhSpnuHCtJBBfes.json\n\nPreview (first 2KB):\n[\n  {\n    \"type\": \"text\",\n    \"text\": \"Here is the complete extraction from the \\\"Vendor Analysis Assessment\\\" sheet. The file is at `/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx` and the full extract was also saved to `/outputs/vendor_data_extract.txt`.\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Sheet: Vendor Analysis Assessment**\\n**Total rows: 386 vendors**\\n\\n**Column Headers (6 columns):**\\n1. Vendor Name\\n2. Department\\n3. Last 12 months Cost (USD)\\n4. 1-line Description on what the Vendor does\\n5. Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs)\\n6. DERIVED-Spend Category\\n\\n---\\n\\n**All 386 data rows (Vendor Name | Department | Annual Spend USD | Description | Suggestion | Spend Category):**\\n\\n- ROW 1: (Blank) | G&A | 137.30 | Unidentified vendor with no name or clear purpose | Terminate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 2: 4I Advisory Services | Professional Services | 71,860.34 | Management advisory firm providing strategic consulting services | Consolidate | Medium Spend\\n- ROW 3: 4I Management Consulting Private Limited | Professional Services | 12,117.49 | Management consulting firm overlapping with 4I Advisory Services | Consolidate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 4: 4Imprint Direct Ltd | Marketing | 2,436.14 | Promotional merchandise supplier | Terminate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 5: 6Sense Insights Inc | Marketing | 75.56 | AI-powered revenue intelligence platform | Terminate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 6: Acclime Corporate Services | G&A | 5,412.87 | Corporate services provider for entity management and compliance | Consolidate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 7: Acclime Usa, Inc | G&A | 4,994.98 | US entity of Acclime providing corporate administration services | Consolidate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 8: Accutrainee Limited | Professional Services | 38,840.80 | Graduate trainee recruitment and placement services | Terminate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 9: Adamma Info Services Private Limited | G&A | 273.33 | Back-office information services provider | Terminate | Low Spend\\n- ROW 10: Adobe Systems Software | SaaS | 3,92\n...\n</persisted-output>"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9ed88350-d5e8-4179-8856-45e53162fa46","uuid":"00dfb984-322d-47cd-aba5-710024077a36","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:52:33.857Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the Excel file at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to extract all vendor data from the \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet. Specifically, I need:\n- Vendor Name\n- Department\n- Annual Spend (or whatever spend column exists)\n- Any other relevant columns (category, contract info, etc.)\n\nUse Python with openpyxl or pandas to read the file and print ALL rows with their column values. Print the column headers first, then all data rows. Make sure to print every single row - do not truncate.\n\nRun the Python script and return the complete output.","agentId":"ae59e1e82d9482af6","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is the complete extraction from the \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet. The file is at `/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx` and the full extract was also saved to `/outputs/vendor_data_extract.txt`.\n\n---\n\n**Sheet: Vendor Analysis Assessment**\n**Total rows: 386 vendors**\n\n**Column Headers (6 columns):**\n1. Vendor Name\n2. Department\n3. Last 12 months Cost (USD)\n4. 1-line Description on what the Vendor does\n5. Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs)\n6. DERIVED-Spend Category\n\n---\n\n**All 386 data rows (Vendor Name | Department | Annual