 | Low Spend\nROW 371: Weking D.O.O. | Facilities | 144093.201148 | Croatian local vendor providing miscellaneous services | Terminate | Medium Spend\nROW 372: Westbrook Advisers | Finance | 15360.3784224 | Financial advisory and consulting services | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 373: Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd. | Facilities | 64373.3640784 | Flexible co-working office space provider | Terminate | Medium Spend\nROW 374: Winmaxi Tours & Travels | Facilities | 1001.362236 | Corporate travel and tour services in India | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 375: Wolt Enterprises Oy | Facilities | 61.739041745 | Food, beverage or hospitality services for office | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 376: Work Easy Space Solutions Private Limited | Facilities | 14913.209029599999 | Managed office and co-working spaces in India | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 377: Workato, Inc. | Engineering | 16101.025599999999 | Enterprise automation and integration platform | Consolidate | Low Spend\nROW 378: Xenon Savjetovanje D.O.O. | Facilities | 164.02312583 | Croatian local vendor providing miscellaneous services | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 379: Yellow Submarine D.O.O. | Facilities | 486.2056435 | Croatian local vendor providing miscellaneous services | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 380: Yoxel, Inc | Engineering | 2043.5964000000001 | API integration and data synchronization services | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 381: ZagrebaäKi Holding D.O.O. | Facilities | 142.829126425 | Croatian local vendor providing miscellaneous services | Terminate | Low Spend\nROW 382: Zagrebtower D.O.O. | Facilities | 183754.4183896 | Zagreb Tower office premises rent and services | Optimize | Medium Spend\nROW 383: Zapier Inc. | Engineering | 166.787560535 | Workflow automation and app integration platform | Consolidate | Low Spend\nROW 384: Zettanet | Engineering | 183.374168765 | Network management and connectivity services | Consolidate | Low Spend\nROW 385: Zivi Napitak D.O.O. | Facilities | 3699.576564 | Food, beverage or hosp