{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_015C2ZSM1TRXkft3mgYm2Djf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Ly4ewCj3V6WM8ifJYXb3HJ","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Compute consolidation group spend totals","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"Using the vendor_data_extract.txt file at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/vendor_data_extract.txt, I need precise spend totals for 23 consolidation groups. Please write and run a Python script that reads the file, parses each row's spend, and sums spend for each of the following vendor groups (match by exact vendor name as listed):\n\nGROUP 1 - CRM & Sales Engagement:\n- Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk\n- Outreach Corporation\n- Cognism Limited\n- Lusha\n- Dun & Bradstreet D.O.O.\n\nGROUP 2 - Office Space & Real Estate:\n- Tog Uk Properties Limited\n- Zagrebtower D.O.O.\n- Innovent Spaces Private Limited\n- Gpt Space & Co\n- Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd.\n- Jones Lang Lasalle (Nsw) Pty Ltd\n- Work Easy Space Solutions Private Limited\n- Common Desk, Llc\n\nGROUP 3 - Travel & Expense (Navan):\n- Navan (Tripactions Inc)\n- Navan, Inc\n\nGROUP 4 - Audit & Accounting:\n- Bdo Llp\n- Grant Thornton\n- Granttree Limited\n- Pricewaterhousecoopers Llp\n- Crowe Horwath Revizija D.O.O.\n\nGROUP 5 - Cloud Infrastructure:\n- Cloudcrossing Bvba\n- Amazon Web Services Llc\n- Cloud Technology Solutions Ltd\n- Microsoft Ireland Operations Limited\n- Amazon Web Services Inc.\n\nGROUP 6 - Employee Health Insurance:\n- Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd\n- Agram Life Osiguranje D.O.O.\n- Care Health Insurance Company Limited\n- Bupa- Supplier\n- Cigna Sg\n- Bupa Australia\n- Allianz Australia Workers' Compensation (Victoria) Limited\n- Allianz Wa\n- Icici Lombard Gic Ltd\n- Cici Prudential Life Insurance Co. Ltd.\n\nGROUP 7 - Financial & M&A Advisory:\n- Rsm Uk Corporate Finance Llp\n- Ss&C Intralinks Inc\n- Houlihan Lokey Advisors, Llc\n- Vector Capital Management Lp\n\nGROUP 8 - HR Outsourcing & Payroll:\n- Hr Solution International Gmbh\n- Harmonic Group Limited\n- Hrsolution International Ag\n- Mercer Limited\n- Ncc Services Limited\n\nGROUP 9 - Marketing Automation & Digital Advertising:\n- Linkedin Ireland Limited\n- Hubspot Ireland Limited\n- Uberflip\n- Google Ireland Limited\n- Mightyhive Ltd\n- Semrush Inc\n\nGROUP 10 - Insurance Brokerage:\n- Jensten Insurance Brokers\n- Shoff Darby Companies\n\nGROUP 11 - Telecoms & Connectivity:\n- Telefonica Global Services Gmbh\n- New Star Networks(Nsn)\n- Hrvatski Telekom D.D.\n- Telemach Hrvatska D.O.O.\n- Vodafone (Australian)\n- T-Mobile\n- Starhub Ltd (Supplier)\n- British Telecommunications\n\nGROUP 12 - Financial Planning SaaS:\n- Kimble Applications Ltd\n- Sage Uk Limited\n- Planful, Inc.\n\nGROUP 13 - Recruitment & Staffing:\n- Accutrainee Limited\n- Mason Frank International Ltd\n- Technet It Recruitment\n- Cedar Recruitment Ltd\n- Info Edge India Limited\n\nGROUP 14 - Legal Services:\n- Bisley Law Ltd\n- Eurofast International Ltd-Greec\n- Visalogic Limited\n- The Virtual Legal Counsel Ltd\n- Pinsent Masons Mpillay Llp\n- Curzon Green Solicitors\n- Quadrant Law Llc\n- Thomas Mansfield Solicitors Limited\n- Lane Ip Limited\n- Franklin, Gringer & Cohen, P.C.\n- Kilgannon & Partners Llp\n- Klg - Kalra Legal Group\n- Induslaw\n\nGROUP 15 - 4I Advisory (Duplicate Entities):\n- 4I Advisory Services\n- 4I Management Consulting Private Limited\n\nGROUP 16 - Work Management Tools:\n- Big Frontier Pty Ltd (Cult Of Monday)\n- Trello\n- Smartsheet Inc.\n- Atlassian Pty Ltd\n\nGROUP 17 - Employee Engagement & Learning:\n- Peakon Aps\n- Performancepro\n- Epignosis Llc\n\nGROUP 18 - Corporate Secretarial:\n- Acclime Corporate Services\n- Acclime Usa, Inc\n- Intertrust Singapore Corporate Services Pte Ltd - Csc\n\nGROUP 19 - Workflow Automation:\n- Workato, Inc.\n- Zapier Inc.\n\nGROUP 20 - Developer Tools & Monitoring:\n- Jetbrains S.R.O.\n- Papertrail Inc\n- Solarwinds, Inc\n\nGROUP 21 - Apple Hardware (Multi-Entity):\n- Apple Retail Uk Ltd\n- Apple Pty Ltd\n- Apple Distribution International Ltd\n- Apple - Amer\n\nGROUP 22 - Allianz Insurance (Duplicate):\n- Allianz Australia Workers' Compensation (Victoria) Limited\n- Allianz Wa\n\nGROUP 23 - Occupational Health Croatia:\n- Specijalisticka Ordinacija Medicine Rada Helena Blazic\n- Specijalisticka Ordinacija Medicine Rada I Sporta Ina Kardos\n- Ustanova Za Medicinu Rada I Sporta Dr. Novacki\n- Ustanova Za Zdravstvenu Skrb P.P.\n\nFor each group, print:\nGROUP_NUMBER | GROUP_NAME | TOTAL_SPEND_USD | VENDOR_COUNT\nAlso print the GRAND_TOTAL across all 23 groups.\n\nRun the script and return the output."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6207,"cache_read_input_tokens":29713,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6207,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9ed88350-d5e8-4179-8856-45e53162fa46","uuid":"a70559c3-bcd1-4140-9b3c-9eb8a25ea9ed"}
{"type":"system","subtype":"task_started","task_id":"a0e33eaa616ad6d2a","tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ly4ewCj3V6WM8ifJYXb3HJ","description":"Compute consolidation group spend totals","task_type":"local_agent","prompt":"Using the vendor_data_extract.txt file at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/vendor_data_extract.txt, I need precise spend totals for 23 consolidation groups. Please write and run a Python script that reads the file, parses each row's spend, and sums spend for each of the following vendor groups (match by exact vendor name as listed):\n\nGROUP 1 - CRM & Sales Engagement:\n- Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk\n- Outreach Corporation\n- Cognism Limited\n- Lusha\n- Dun & Bradstreet D.O.O.\n\nGROUP 2 - Office Space & Real Estate:\n- Tog Uk Properties Limited\n- Zagrebtower D.O.O.\n- Innovent Spaces Private Limited\n- Gpt Space & Co\n- Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd.\n- Jones Lang Lasalle (Nsw) Pty Ltd\n- Work Easy Space Solutions Private Limited\n- Common Desk, Llc\n\nGROUP 3 - Travel & Expense (Navan):\n- Navan (Tripactions Inc)\n- Navan, Inc\n\nGROUP 4 - Audit & Accounting:\n- Bdo Llp\n- Grant Thornton\n- Granttree Limited\n- Pricewaterhousecoopers Llp\n- Crowe Horwath Revizija D.O.O.\n\nGROUP 5 - Cloud Infrastructure:\n- Cloudcrossing Bvba\n- Amazon Web Services Llc\n- Cloud Technology Solutions Ltd\n- Microsoft Ireland Operations Limited\n- Amazon Web Services Inc.\n\nGROUP 6 - Employee Health Insurance:\n- Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd\n- Agram Life Osiguranje D.O.O.\n- Care Health Insurance Company Limited\n- Bupa- Supplier\n- Cigna Sg\n- Bupa Australia\n- Allianz Australia Workers' Compensation (Victoria) Limited\n- Allianz Wa\n- Icici Lombard Gic Ltd\n- Cici Prudential Life Insurance Co. Ltd.\n\nGROUP 7 - Financial & M&A Advisory:\n- Rsm Uk Corporate Finance Llp\n- Ss&C Intralinks Inc\n- Houlihan Lokey Advisors, Llc\n- Vector Capital Management Lp\n\nGROUP 8 - HR Outsourcing & Payroll:\n- Hr Solution International Gmbh\n- Harmonic Group Limited\n- Hrsolution Intern