{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ly4ewCj3V6WM8ifJYXb3HJ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 23 groups matched perfectly — zero unmatched vendors. Here are the results:\n\n---\n\n**GROUP | GROUP NAME | TOTAL_SPEND_USD | VENDOR_COUNT**\n\n| # | Group Name | Total Spend (USD) | Vendors |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | CRM & Sales Engagement | $3,156,660.40 | 5 |\n| 2 | Office Space & Real Estate | $827,833.50 | 8 |\n| 3 | Travel & Expense (Navan) | $415,912.91 | 2 |\n| 4 | Audit & Accounting | $412,219.19 | 5 |\n| 5 | Cloud Infrastructure | $390,710.41 | 5 |\n| 6 | Employee Health Insurance | $238,406.18 | 10 |\n| 7 | Financial & M&A Advisory | $226,932.25 | 4 |\n| 8 | HR Outsourcing & Payroll | $161,707.66 | 5 |\n| 9 | Marketing Automation & Digital Advertising | $161,420.08 | 6 |\n| 10 | Insurance Brokerage | $152,800.20 | 2 |\n| 11 | Telecoms & Connectivity | $147,711.78 | 8 |\n| 12 | Financial Planning SaaS | $127,461.57 | 3 |\n| 13 | Recruitment & Staffing | $121,014.48 | 5 |\n| 14 | Legal Services | $112,553.52 | 13 |\n| 15 | 4I Advisory (Duplicate Entities) | $83,977.83 | 2 |\n| 16 | Work Management Tools | $76,023.82 | 4 |\n| 17 | Employee Engagement & Learning | $27,958.60 | 3 |\n| 18 | Corporate Secretarial | $17,767.48 | 3 |\n| 19 | Workflow Automation | $16,267.81 | 2 |\n| 20 | Developer Tools & Monitoring | $8,148.80 | 3 |\n| 21 | Apple Hardware (Multi-Entity) | $8,256.02 | 4 |\n| 22 | Allianz Insurance (Duplicate) | $7,069.34 | 2 |\n| 23 | Occupational Health Croatia | $191.67 | 4 |\n| **GRAND TOTAL** | | **$6,899,005.49** | **118 vendor entries** |\n\n**Key observations:**\n\n- Every vendor name matched exactly — no unresolved lookups.\n- Group 1 (CRM) dominates at $3.16M, representing 45.8% of the grand total on its own.\n- Group 22 (Allianz Insurance Duplicate) is a subset of Group 6 (Employee Health Insurance) — the two Allianz entities ($7,069.34) are already counted within Group 6's $238,406.18 total, so the grand total double-counts them by $7,069.34 if Groups 6 and 22 are both used independently.\n- The grand total of $6,899,005.49 is slightly higher than the $6.23M previously noted in project memory (STEP 07), likely because this run includes all 23 groups including the duplicate Allianz group."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a0e33eaa616ad6d2a (use SendMessage with to: 'a0e33eaa616ad6d2a' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 16644\ntool_uses: 4\nduration_ms: 91953</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9ed88350-d5e8-4179-8856-45e53162fa46","uuid":"6065fd3f-7090-4a9d-b84c-8921493763ae","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:58:40.799Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Using the vendor_data_extract.txt file at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/vendor_data_extract.txt, I need precise spend totals for 23 consolidation groups. Please write and run a Python script that reads the file, parses each row's spend, and sums spend for each of the following vendor groups (match by exact vendor name as listed):\n\nGROUP 1 - CRM & Sales Engagement:\n- Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk\n- Outreach Corporation\n- Cognism Limited\n- Lusha\n- Dun & Bradstreet D.O.O.\n\nGROUP 2 - Office Space & Real Estate:\n- Tog Uk Properties Limited\n- Zagrebtower D.O.O.\n- Innovent Spaces Private Limited\n- Gpt Space & Co\n- Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd.\n- Jones Lang Lasalle (Nsw) Pty Ltd\n- Work Easy Space Solutions Private Limited\n- Common Desk, Llc\n\nGROUP 3 - Travel & Expense (Navan):\n- Navan (Tripactions Inc)\n- Navan, Inc\n\nGROUP 4 - Audit & Accounting:\n- Bdo Llp\n- Grant Thornton\n- Granttree Limited\n- Pricewaterhousecoopers Llp\n- Crowe Horwath Revizija D.O.O.\n\nGROUP 5 - Cloud Infrastructure:\n- Cloudcrossing Bvba\n- Amazon Web Services Llc\n- Cloud Technology Solutions Ltd\n- Microsoft Ireland Operations Limited\n- Amazon Web Services Inc.\n\nGROUP 6 - Employee Health Insurance:\n- Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd\n- Agram Life Osiguranje D.O